> Sports Blue Jays try to force deciding Game 7 vs Royals in ALCS Kansas City Royals catcher Salvador Perez plays guitar with his bat during batting practice at Kauffman Stadium in Kansas City, Mo., Thursday, Oct. 22, 2015.
